Package com.facebook.buck.rules.modern

Interface ClassInfo<T extends AddsToRuleKey>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultClassInfo
    public interface ClassInfo<T extends AddsToRuleKey>
    ClassInfo is used by ModernBuildRule to extract information from an AddsToRuleKey instance. It computes various things (rulekeys, deps, etc) by iterating over all the fields of the AddsToRuleKey.
